Meet with Meshif in the Outer Gardens

Though Elias was found to be immortal, we managed to escape his palace and seize the Sightless Eye along the way. Now we need to reconvene and sort out our options. As an undying thrall of the returned Mother of Sanctuary, I'm sure we'll be seeing Elias again soon.
